long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Saws are a fun arcade game where we try to progress and pay attention to the saws we come across with a square ninja.

There is a square ninja in the game. We can control this square ninja. With the ninja that we can control, we try to move forward by paying attention to the saws that we encounter. We earn points by progressing carefully. We continue the game by maintaining our high score goal with the points we have achieved. Saws have emerged as a game of skill that has been prepared for us, those who love children's games, as it is fun and challenging for us.

To swipe Install this extension to play the Saws Game or offline with no additional downloads and no ads. 

You can contact us at support@724fun.com and share your thoughts and problems

After clicking the add the game to chrome button, you can find the game in the extensions section. If you wish, you can visit 724fun.com. If you wish, you can play again and if you want to remove it, you can remove it from the extensions section.
